    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article in The Arts on Monday about the success Ashton Kutcher and Jason Goldberg have had with their Katalyst Films production company referred incorrectly to the assets of Merv Griffin, another successful producer to whom Mr. Kutcher was compared in the article. Although Mr. Griffin did indeed once own the Beverly Hilton hotel, he sold it in 2003.</p>
      </block>
